//These functions scan through properties in JOURNAL objects, to first build matrix then find a correllation coefficient  
// between events strings and the squirrel boolean. The construction of the matrix 'Table' is in the following form
// [ no event found, squirrel false ; event found, squirrel false ; no event found, squirrel true ; event found, squirrel true]
